title: Trick-or-treating in Lake County
text: Add a message (optional) Success - Article sent! close Grayslake residents Bailey Truitt, left, dressed as Dorothy from "The Wizard of Oz" and her twin brother Lucas as superhero Robin. Grayslake's trick-or-treat hours are 4-7 p.m. Oct. 31 this year. Paul Valade | Staff Photographer, 2013 Molly Micelli of Libertyville is dressed as a kitty as she trick-or-treats with her parents in downtown Libertyville. Libertyville's trick-or-treating hours this year are 4-8 p.m. on Oct. 31.
